<p class="ql-align-center">购买2杯饮品，高价饮品结算，低价饮品赠送</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200824/b67fa5336bd34b459a470c7e422734ad.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
